hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外<br />\n生女既父母絕對應該草定錢幫個女脫毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男朋友勁多毛，佢話第時生女一定同佢laser脫哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇絲打可以分享點美白underarm, 本身唔白又易積黑色素，打完laser脫毛叫好少少但都係黑黑地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c2dc1c87c01478cf041d90f01babb34a4e994b","tid":400793,"uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T22:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本女人由眼睫毛打落就唔應該有任何一條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外<br />\n生女既父母絕對應該草定錢幫個女脫毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男朋友勁多毛，佢話第時生女一定同佢laser脫哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇絲打可以分享點美白underarm, 本身唔白又易積黑色素，打完laser脫毛叫好少少但都係黑黑地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做埋cps，買左40次，做左10次左右，d粒粒退得少少同埋兩邊明顯白，但就中間仲係黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 治療師話要做二十次以上先明顯，放長雙眼睇。"},{"pid":"2abb69c0bb61ab97ec37d91dad8c099c6b71e1ed","tid":400793,"uid":49274,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T22:32:41.000Z","msg":"知唔知脫毛幾錢，唔講細公司續次買，同咩388任脫假鬼人果d。<br />\n大公司全手全腳各接近兩萬，underarm同upper lip大約9000，手指同手背另計錢，全腳又兩萬，未計腳趾。仲有比基尼線等等又萬萬聲，仲話underarm 要白&hellip; 一次平平地600 做40次以上先明顯(已經計左折扣)。<br />\n我相信明星果d，一係本身無毛，一係拎野搽落去幫underarm化妝。"},{"pid":"db4c4cec9ce0beca083cb626f3e95a9711379348","tid":400793,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T22:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女權撚表示身體自主啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都on9..."},{"pid":"11ec40b5267b53ea82b67e7019128c43a0c745e3","tid":400793,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T22:36:22.000Z","msg":"個post有陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c095d899374dcdc8e266b12edc088f9262b9a988","tid":400793,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T22:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解男人可以著背心露格肋底毛 女人唔得<br />\n但男人好似健美先生咁無毛又覺得係正常<br />\n明明係人體正常毛髮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解女人唔可以係沙灘什至係當街露lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888f57d1ad40df9b4cf4dda8ad6a4358c57b4ffb","tid":400793,"uid":125079,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班男人唔洗剃唔會麻煩到自己就係度講咩都得"},{"pid":"739161fead2a259c838a5ead9964a29bc262c752","tid":400793,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班男人唔洗剃唔會麻煩到自己就係度講咩都得</blockquote><br />\n死撚開啦<br />\n女人<br />\n上badykingdom la on9"},{"pid":"e778e95d7098317024a33515f6f71d7e0fcaba21","tid":400793,"uid":16528,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解男人可以著背心露格肋底毛 女人唔得<br />\n但男人好似健美先生咁無毛又覺得係正常<br />\n明明係人體正常毛髮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解女人著男裝會叫中性打扮<br />\n男著女裝叫易服癖？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n體毛生長黎無得揀 易服癖係自己選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br /